Description_lang: Icy Enchantments teleport to a random enemy and channel a Frozen Tempest, increasing their vulnerability to attacks by $s8%.The tempest creates a dome of frost, inflicting $213085s1 Frost damage to units inside and pushing them towards the outer edge of the dome. Players who cross this threshold will be stunned in place, creating a block of ice that must be destroyed before the stun is removed.
AuraDescription_lang: Damage taken inceased by $s8%.Channeling a Frozen Tempest.
